  <p>The key insight: <strong>Riverpod and Atoms are architectural siblings</strong> &mdash; both use implicit dependency graphs with push-based propagation, just in different frameworks (Flutter vs SwiftUI). Jotai shares the implicit graph but uses pull-based lazy evaluation instead.</p>
